profile:
Whitby Landscaping and Gardening will provide individualized flower bed care and maintenance 
specific for your residential property or commercial business. Provides design and garden clean-up services. 

Specializing in sod replacement projects. 

Removal of the top layer of turf using a sod cutter, disposal of the material, adding a layer of screened topsoil & leveling, and installing Kentucky bluegrass sod. 

We provide Landscaping and Gardening Services for residents of Whitby, Brooklin, Ajax, Oshawa, and Pickering Ontario.
